Title: Daddy's Little Girl
Plot: The CSIs investigate the stabbing of a motocross racer who was about to leave town with a young woman he had been living with.  Also, Nick comes closer to finding the truth about his kidnapping.
GuestStars: Louise Lombard, Wallace Langham, Liz Vassey, Aimee Graham, Taylor Cole, Mitch Pileggi, Rebecca Staab, Joe Manganiello, Archie Kao, Sheeri Rappaport, Gerald McCullouch, David Berman, Timothy Lee DePriest
